title: Update On Bobby's CDL Test + Country Lyric Or Bumper Sticker? + Amy Talks With Tim McGraw And Tyler Hubbard
itunes:title: Update On Bobby's CDL Test + Country Lyric Or Bumper Sticker? + Amy Talks With Tim McGraw And Tyler Hubbard
description:
Bobby gives us a big update on his CDL test. Bobby reads a phrase and the show has to guess if it’s the lyrics to a country song or a slogan from a bumper sticker. Amy interviews Tim McGraw and Tyler Hubbard of Florida Georgia Line about their new song “Undivided” and has a question about Tim McGraw’s movie Roles. Bobby talks to Amy about her going bridesmaids shopping with Caitlin. He also talks about what Amy’s son is doing in the wedding.
